                  <h3>Book Summary</h3>
         <div id="summary" class="storylocation linkLocation">
                        <div id="res828499239" class="bucketwrap listtext">
                              <div class="bucket">
                                    <p>The award-winning New York Times food editor celebrates the art of Sunday suppers and the joys of gathering with friends and family, complementing simple, traditional recipes for small and larger groups with tips about rendering classics distinctive. Illustrations.</p>
